cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.NI, cs.DC

The paper discusses a new approach for streaming 360 VR videos, which involves spatially dividing the videos into multiple tiles and prioritizing the tiles in the Field of View (FoV). This involves techniques related to multimedia (cs.MM), graphics (cs.GR), computer vision (cs.CV), networking (cs.NI), and distributed computing (cs.DC). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.NI, and cs.DC, in that order.
